quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  83,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  83,1,tabahi hai dandi maarny walon ke liye
  83,2,jin ka haal yeh hai ke jab logon se letay hain to poora poora letay hain
  83,3,aur jab un ko naap kar ya toal kar dete hain to inhen ghata dete hain
  83,4,"kya yeh log nahi samajte ke aik barray din ,"
  83,5,yeh utha kar laaye jaane walay hain ?
  83,6,uss din jabkay sab log Rab alaalmin ke samnay kharray hon ge
  83,7,"hargiz nahi, yaqeenan bad karon ka nama aamaal qaid khanaay ke daftar mein hai"
  83,8,aur tumhe kya maloom ke woh qaid khanaay ka daftar kya hai ?
  83,9,aik kitaab hai likhi hui
  83,10,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  83,11,jo roz jaza ko jutlatay hain
  83,12,aur ussay nahi jhutlata magar har woh shakhs jo hadd se guzar jaane wala bad amal hai
  83,13,ussay jab hamari ayaat sunai jati hain to kehta hai yeh to aglay waqton ki kahaniyan hain
  83,14,"hargiz nahi, balkay darasal inn logon ke dilon par inn ke buray aamaal ka zang charh gaya hai"
  83,15,"hargiz nahi, bilyaqeen uss roz yeh apne Rab ki deed se mahroom rakhay jayen ge"
  83,16,phir yeh jahannum mein ja parrin ge
  83,17,phir inn se kaha jaye ga ke yeh wohi cheez hai jisay tum jhtlaya karte thay
  83,18,"hargiz nahi, be shak naik admion ka nama aamaal buland paya logon ke daftar mein hai"
  83,19,aur tumhe kya khabar ke kya hai woh buland paya logon ka daftar ?
  83,20,aik likhi hui kitaab hai
  83,21,jis ki nighdasht MaqarRab farishtay karte hain
  83,22,be shak naik log barray mazay mein hon ge
  83,23,onchi masnadon(stage)par baithy nazare kar rahay hon ge
  83,24,un ke cheharon par tum khushhali ki ronaqe mehsoos karo ge
  83,25,un ko nafees tareen sir band sharaab pilayi jaye gi jis par mushk ki mohar lagi hogi
  83,26,jo log dosaron par baazi le jana chahtay hon woh iss cheez ko haasil karne mein baazi le jaane ki koshish karen
  83,27,uss sharaab mein Tasneem ki ameezash hogi
  83,28,yeh aik chashma hai jis ke pani ke sath MaqarRab log sharaab piyen ge
  83,29,mujrim log duniya mein imaan laane walon ka mazaq uratay thay
  83,30,jab unn ke paas se guzarte to ankhen maar maar kar unn ki taraf isharay karte thay
  83,31,apne gharon ki taraf palatne to mazay letay hue palatne thay
  83,32,aur jab inhen dekhte to kehte thay ke yeh behke hue log hain
  83,33,halaank woh unn par nigaran bana kar nahi beje gay thay
  83,34,aaj imaan laane walay kufar par hans rahay hain
  83,35,masnadon par baithy hue un ka haal dekh rahay hain
  83,36,mil gaya na kafiroon ko unn harkato ka sawab jo woh kya karte thay
